Description:
Agreement
  with Citibank N.A. dated 12/13/02 to receive 2.41% per year times the
  notional amount. In exchange for that periodic payment, upon a default event
  by AOL Time Warner Inc., the Fund agrees to pay Citibank N.A. the notional
  amount of the swap. To receive that payment, Citibank N.A. must deliver a
  bond (with par value equal to the notional of the swap) issued by AOL Time
  Warner Inc.

  deliver a bond (with par value equal to the notional of the swap) issued by
